      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "And he did that which was evil in the sight of the Lord: he departed not all his days from the sins of Jeroboam the son of Nebat, who made Israel to sin.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " The writer does not seem to regard Menahem as either better or worse than his predecessors. The usual formula suffices to describe the moral and religious aspect of his reign. 2 Kings 15:18",
